casebody.data:
In the MATTER OF Melvin M. MARIN, a Suspended Attorney. Attorney Grievance Committee for the Third Judicial Department, Respondent;
v.
Melvin M. Marin, Appellant. Court of Appeals of New York. September 6, 2018

Appeal dismissed without costs, by the Court sua sponte, upon the ground that the February 2018 Appellate Division order appealed from does not finally determine the proceeding within the meaning of the Constitution.
